OL,3,CTata bosses trigger countdown to Port
OL,4,CTalbot job losses
OL,6,FIt comes after the announcement last
OL,7,Fmonth that nearly 3,000 jobs will be
OL,8,Faxed in the coming years ` the
OL,9,Fmajority of which are expected to be
OL,10,Fat its Port Talbot plant.
OL,12,FTata announced in January that it
OL,13,Fplans to close Port Talbot's two blast
OL,14,Ffurnaces in a move towards a of
OL,15,Fsteelmaking.
OL,17,FThis method, although better for the
OL,18,Fclimate, is less labour intensive and
OL,19,Fwill therefore require less workers.
