OL,3,CTata bosses trigger countdown to Port
OL,4,CTalbot job losses
OL,6,FA Tata Steel spokesperson said: "Today
OL,7,Fwe have started the formal
OL,8,Fconsultation process with our Trades
OL,9,FUnion partners regarding the proposed
OL,10,Frestructuring of the UK business.
OL,12,F"This information sharing and
OL,13,Fconsultation process will continue for
OL,14,Fa minimum of 45 days, through which we
OL,15,Fhope to have an open and constructive
OL,16,Fdialogue regarding the challenges the
OL,17,Fbusiness is facing."
