OL,3,CTata bosses trigger countdown to Port
OL,4,CTalbot job losses
OL,6,FPeter Hughes, Unite regional secretary
OL,7,Ffor Wales, said: "The proposed would
OL,8,Fbe devastating for the workforce, Port
OL,9,FTalbot and and would leave the UK
OL,10,Funable to make virgin steel.
OL,12,F"Unite will be entering into
OL,13,Fconsultation with Tata over these
OL,14,Fplans and will be crystal clear that
OL,15,Fthey should not be happening. We
OL,16,Fcannot have rushed talks and the
OL,17,Fstatutory consultation period of 45
OL,18,Fdays is entirely inadequate given the
OL,19,Fsheer scale of the proposed job losses
OL,20,Fand the knock-on effects they would
OL,21,Fhave.
